      <description>&lt;p&gt;The HTML Presentation Framework&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Reveal.js is a framework for easily creating beautiful adaptive presentations using HTML. You can create slides with Markdown, HTML, or any other web technology.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;key-features&#34; class=&#34;scroll-mt-8 group&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Key features&#xA;  &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#key-features&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;no-underline hidden opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 !text-inherit group-hover:inline-block&#34;&#xA;        aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to this heading&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg&#xA;  xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&#xA;  width=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  height=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xA;  stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;lucide lucide-link w-4 h-4 block&#34;&#xA;  viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Markdown&lt;/strong&gt;: Write your slides in Markdown and let Reveal.js convert them to HTML.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Themes&lt;/strong&gt;: Choose from a variety of themes or create your own to customize the look of your presentation.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsive&lt;/strong&gt;: Create presentations that adapt to different screen sizes and devices.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PDF Export&lt;/strong&gt;: Export your presentation to PDF for easy sharing and printing.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Keyboard and Touch Shortcuts&lt;/strong&gt;: Navigate your presentation with keyboard shortcuts, swipe, tap, and pinch for a smoother experience.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speaker Notes&lt;/strong&gt;: Add speaker notes to your slides for a better presentation experience.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy to deploy&lt;/strong&gt;: Host your presentation on any web server or use GitHub Pages for free hosting.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;links&#34; class=&#34;scroll-mt-8 group&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Links&#xA;  &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#links&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;no-underline hidden opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 !text-inherit group-hover:inline-block&#34;&#xA;        aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to this heading&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg&#xA;  xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&#xA;  width=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  height=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xA;  stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;lucide lucide-link w-4 h-4 block&#34;&#xA;  viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Demo, try it using the smartphone too:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
